pageContext.claim: “It’s been totally discredited. Even Democrats agree, that it’s been discredited...."I don’t think we have to go much further than to say that they’ve been misled because the dossier is a phony deal and so much of what’s been done is just bad stuff.”
pageContext.analysis: Democrats have not said that the dossier has been "totally discredited." Some elements appear to be wrong but other parts have been on target.
